item.description: Wizkid's family has released the funeral arrangement for the singer's late mother, Mrs Jane Dolapo BalogunAccording to details provided on a viral flyer, the wake and tribute night will take place on Thursday, October 12, followed by a funeral service on Friday, October 13The recent update has stirred reactions from many of Wizkid's fans amid his silence on social mediaMonths after music star Wizkid's mother, Mrs Jane Dolapo Balogun, passed on, the singer's family has released details about her funeral arrangement.

item.title: Zendaya's Low-Cut Goddess Gown Nearly Plunged to Her Belly Button
item.description: If there's one thing we can say about Zendaya's style, it's that it doesn't fit into any single box. One day, she'll be wearing a classic LBD, and the next...a full-on robot suit. In other words, the girl has range, and just yesterday, she showed off her sartorial versatility once again while sporting two very different looks in one night.  First, Zendaya attended the Essence Black Women in Hollywood award ceremony dressed in a sheer silver corset with delicate floral embroidery and paired with baggy medium-wash cuffed jeans.
